{"tid":164239,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"57%美國年輕人視川普為「非法總統」　少數族裔最賭爛","createTime":"2017-03-20T14:02:57.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-20T14:48:49.000Z","uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"8ede46a9fe4a879101da2f8fada9ce0d4b9ce914","tid":164239,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-20T14:02:57.000Z","msg":"2017年03月20日 21:45<br />\n國際中心／綜合報導<br />\n<img src=\"http://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/2275/d2275716.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F2275%2Fd2275716.jpg&h=a85e0902&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">美國最新出爐的一份民調顯示，有57%的美國年輕人不挺川普，甚至視他為非法總統，其中包括4分之3的非裔，以及多數的拉丁裔與亞裔族群。</span><br />\n<br />\nGenForward與美聯社-NORC公共事務研究中心合作，調查1833位年齡在18~30位之間的美國年輕人，對象包括516名非裔、504名拉丁裔、277名亞裔、505名非拉丁裔白人。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">在白人的部分，有53%的年輕白人認為川普是合法總統</span>，但在這個族群中仍有55%不滿川普到目前為止的表現，整體調查而言，62%的年輕人都不滿川普的施政，只有22%的人滿意。<br />\n<br />\n根據調查，10個年輕人中有8人認為川普在提出政策方面表現不佳，而10人中則有7人對他的總統風度抱有負面觀感，但專家表示，這些民調受訪者在訪談中表示，他們不必然會因反對一個政黨的候選人而去投另一黨候選人，這也是年輕美國人的明顯趨勢。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.ettoday.net/news/20170320/888481.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.ettoday.net%2Fnews%2F20170320%2F888481.htm&d=FZDcFY5BXo0CBgddFpFX56NGKT0mDZcTD8WJHRevFdc%3D&h=df98fc3e\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.ettoday.net/news/20170320/888481.htm</a>"},{"pid":"d6b61a7fe59e54e644e3eaca217d0add82b1ae6e","tid":164239,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-20T14:07:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"28cbc48f0ccfcae4e0e6cee9216210dedaa235e5","tid":164239,"uid":40216,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-20T14:22:35.000Z","msg":"唔中意咪走咯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"179214360e80bff2c77e17de73e3c2981f968c20","tid":164239,"uid":82929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":